<span id="freeTextContainer4603462624958514535">It hit me. I... <br/><br/>A one act play in real time that deals with suicide, love, and the meaning of life. I never thought it would resonate with me as much as it did. Extraordinarily well-crafted. Some idiot crossed out and modified lines with a pencil in my library copy. Who would mess with such a great script?</span>

          </span>
