        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2456775239" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10216907866028839061">Marsha Norman’s play is about an epileptic woman, Jessie Cates, who has had enough of living and is tired of losing control of her life. She prepares her mother for her suicide while her mother tries to talk her out of it. Very moving!<br/><br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


